This paper discusses natural language processing and understanding, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning and artificial intelligence techniques to achieve language understanding, which falls under the categories of AI (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of a database and robot command and control, which falls under the categories of information retrieval (cs.IR) and robotics (cs.RO). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL, followed by cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, and cs.RO.
